{"tid":1319364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mina因病停工　TWICE開騷感觸落淚","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T23:49:24.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"21425f8dda68f65dbea49d8ee357c3a340eac37e","tid":1319364,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女團TWICE的日本成員Mina本月5日因健康理由而缺席活動，日前所屬的JYP事務所指Mina最近突然對舞台感到極度緊張及不安，需要停工接受治療及靜養，故不會參與組合接下來的世界巡唱。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE前晚以8人陣容在新加坡舉行演唱會，與一萬名粉絲見面，而成員在結尾講感受，談到因病而缺席的Mina時，一度都忍不住爆喊，同是日本出身的Sana說：「我知道了身邊人對我來說有多重要，希望大家記住TWICE永遠是8個人。」而其他成員亦跟粉絲說：「我們無論甚麼時候、無論在甚麼地方，都會是8個人。」希望粉絲不要忘記Mina，而不少網民及粉絲都留言送祝福，希望Mina早日康復歸隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=1ad99164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina近日宣布因病而缺席組合巡唱，TWICE前日在新加坡開騷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=42c7384c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定延在演唱會尾後時忍不住落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=c3e25d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana談到Mina因為健康問題而缺席時，一度傷心落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=f2fa6a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE前日以7人陣容在新加坡開騷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=2bc1a613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隊長志效亦喊到眼紅紅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190715133024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715123820382-0715_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190715133024&h=aae4c334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina最近突然對舞台感到極度緊張及不安，需要停工接受治療及休息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eo6zVEf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEo6zVEf.gif&h=01e7238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跳唱多首歌曲。"},{"pid":"48cb398d1de0e5163a5226fd467847c57467e619","tid":1319364,"uid":60256,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"Twice唔係不嬲8個人咩？"},{"pid":"aca5af90f2f2e01bfa18ffc678e6e463388976f2","tid":1319364,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"唔係咁爽下哇=.="},{"pid":"dd9dd3a72544ea866c2c3e271784f29a104a8626","tid":1319364,"uid":213300,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"48cb398d1de0e5163a5226fd467847c57467e619","tid":1319364,"uid":60256,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"Twice唔係不嬲8個人咩？"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:00:12.000Z","msg":"55<br />\nmomo,mina,sana,子瑜,志效,彩瑛,定延,娜璉"},{"pid":"9da0a70bb67340ee624ab930103a77cf1695d56b","tid":1319364,"uid":74065,"like":0,